headline: 1 Semiconductor Stock to Keep an Eye On and 2 to Turn Down
summary: Semiconductors are the picks and shovels of modern technology. The way we live and work is also changing with AI, which is creating secular demand for more powerful chips. This theme has led to decent stock price performance as the industry’s six-month gain of 4.5% has nearly mirrored the S&P 500.
